re":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T03:04:33.000Z","msg":"比阿姐做特首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24077db7c42d74916baf78d99627e4c965d6a8a6","tid":537193,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c936561d5901f0bc4d8a022923dfe0c336bdf7e5","tid":537193,"uid":42009,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"11069c3fbdcf675f41ed12f1dd49a8801ea2499a","tid":537193,"uid":73366,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T15:19:25.000Z","msg":"成日營住tvb啲人好唔妥余詠珊，以前620陳志雲年代都未係咁差，一到咗余詠珊掌權，就一落千丈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T16:23:06.000Z","msg":"自己唔得就已經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要夾硬推自己帶來D垃圾上位阻住其他努力既人，正常人都唔妥啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要照顧堆佢老公公司班友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n帶堆隔離鄰舍返工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T08:14:55.000Z","msg":"如果真係做掂嘅話，交邊個都可以做到好成績，而唔係來來去去都係自己友。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢而家都已經搞到成個無線「亞視+有線化」，成個台本來係對外開放，而家反而越來越自我封閉，唔係話要訪問埋對家嘅節目，但係畀我嘅感覺係越來越單一，只係講下自已大台嘅消息，外界嘅消息就一字不提。<br />\n可能會話：「咁係因為人地版稅問題而唔可以咁做，有乜計？」，ok我都仲可以同你講得通，但係電影呢？演唱會呢？就算唔自己嘅都唔使搞到乜都唔關事咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ebd9650e7e20f350af39e994fbc529dc94d8680","tid":537193,"uid":156068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T14:28:07.000Z","msg":"d劇ge質素都無進步"}]}